{"tid":2202840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"弱智身分證？","createTime":"2020-09-15T02:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T02:25:22.000Z","uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8d090dbeed6782398873d5076e511ef3c7a695aa","tid":2202840,"uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:25:22.000Z","msg":"今日陪條仔去法國照胃鏡，因為佢上星期一急性胃痛入左急症室。 咁去到就要轉介信(姑娘應該叫約期紙掛)@@<br />\n<br />\n當我地等緊身份證登記嗰時，我隔離行左條幾靚女嘅港女，我男朋友明明胃痛都係咁𥄫女。𥄫到個故娘都咳左幾聲。<br />\n<br />\n之後，我地聽到有個姑娘對住條女講，&rdquo;弱智，身份證&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我條仔望住我。笑到胃痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}